OL,6,FIrish premier Simon Harris has
OL,7,Fdescribed the Stardust tragedy as "one
OL,8,Fof the darkest moments in our history".
OL,10,FHe made the comments after a jury
OL,11,Freturned unlawful killing verdicts for
OL,12,Fall 48 people killed in the 1981
OL,13,Fdisaster.
OL,15,FThe devastating blaze at the Stardust
OL,16,Fnightclub in Artane, north Dublin,
OL,17,Fbroke out in the early hours of
OL,18,FValentine's Day.
