OL,6,F"A heartbreaking tragedy because of
OL,7,Fthe lives that were lost, the families
OL,8,Fthat were changed forever, and the
OL,9,Flong, drawn-out struggle for justice
OL,10,Fthat followed," Simon Harris said.
OL,12,FHe remembered those who lost their
OL,13,Flives and paid tribute to their
OL,14,Ffamilies for pursuing truth and
OL,15,Fjustice "to ensure that such a
OL,16,Fdisaster never happens again".
OL,18,FThe verdict follows over 11 days of
OL,19,Fjury deliberations.
