OL,6,FThe jury foreman said they had reached
OL,7,Fthe same verdict into the deaths of
OL,8,Feach individual, which will be
OL,9,Fdelivered after matters relating to
OL,10,Ftheir identification and cause of
OL,11,Fdeath are dealt with.JDirected by
OL,12,FIreland's attorney general, the
OL,13,Finquests have been the longest held in
OL,14,Fthe Republic, with proceedings
OL,15,Fbeginning a year ago.JSome Stardust
OL,16,Ffamily members jumped to their feet
OL,17,Fand clapped at the verdict, while some
OL,18,Fsat in their seats and were moved to
OL,19,Ftears.JOthers embraced each other as
OL,20,Fsoon as "unlawful killing" was said by
OL,21,Fthe foreman of the jury.
