OL,6,FCoroner Dr Myra Cullinane paid tribute
OL,7,Fto the "persistence and commitment" of
OL,8,Fthe families who had campaigned for
OL,9,Ffresh inquests.
OL,11,F"To the families I acknowledge the
OL,12,Fdeaths of these 48 young people is a
OL,13,Fsource of ongoing grief to those who
OL,14,Floved them and it remains the defining
OL,15,Floss of their lives," she said.
