OL,6,F"However, I hope that family members
OL,7,Fwill have taken some solace from the
OL,8,Ffact that these fresh inquests were
OL,9,Fheld, that the facts surrounding the
OL,10,Fdeaths were examined in detail, that
OL,11,Fmoving testimony was heard from many
OL,12,Fof those involved in the events of the
OL,13,Fnight and, most importantly, that you
OL,14,Fthe families felt fully involved in
OL,15,Fproceedings, however difficult it was
OL,16,Fto hear all of the evidence.
OL,18,F"The fact that these inquests have
OL,19,Fbeen held at all is in no small part
OL,20,Fdue to the persistence and commitment
OL,21,Fof families over the years.
