OL,6,F"And, finally, we remember those 48
OL,7,Fyoung people who lost their lives on
OL,8,Fthat fateful night. It is their lives
OL,9,Fthat we've sought to vindicate by way
OL,10,Fof these inquests."
OL,12,FThe Taoiseach has said the Irish
OL,13,Fgovernment will consider the verdict
OL,14,Fin full, and the recommendations of
OL,15,Fthe jury.
OL,17,F"I want to acknowledge and thank the
OL,18,Fcoroner, and her team and the jurors,"
OL,19,Fhe said.
